@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Scroll";
}

<div class="fade-in">
    <h1 class="display-4">📜 The Privacy Scroll 📜</h1>
    <hr class="gold-divider">

    <p>
        Hear ye, hear ye! Traveler, as you embark upon your journey through the hallowed grounds of Traveler’s Haven, know this:
        your secrets shall be guarded as if they were the lost runes of an ancient kingdom.
    </p>

    <h3>⚖️ The Laws of Privacy</h3>
    <p>
        We value your trust and honor, and thus, we vow to protect any information you share with us.
        Your Email, Name, and any other sacred knowledge will not be sold, traded, or given to the dark sorcerers of the internet.
    </p>

    <h3>🔍 What Data We Collect</h3>
    <ul class="no-bullets">
        <li>📜 Your Username – for identifying your legacy.</li>
        <li>📧 Your Email – for sending messages from the Guildmaster (optional).</li>
        <li>🔑 Your Password – kept in a fortress of encryption (hashed & secured).</li>
        <li>⚔️ Battle Logs – anonymous analytics to improve your experience.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>🛡️ How Your Data is Protected</h3>
    <p>
        We use secure encryption, battle-tested firewalls, and two-factor authentication to guard your information like
        an unbreakable stronghold. No mere mortal nor hacker shall breach our defenses.
    </p>

    <h3>🚪 Your Rights as a Traveler</h3>
    <p>
        You have the right to:
    </p>
    <ul class="no-bullets">
        <li>📜 Request a copy of your data.</li>
        <li>🔥 Purge your presence (delete your account and all records).</li>
        <li>⚔️ Choose your fate (opt-out of notifications & tracking).</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>
        🧭️ Third-Party Kingdoms</h4>
    <p>
        We do not share your data with dark forces or shady merchants. However, we may use noble allies (trusted third-party services)
        to enhance your journey.
    </p>

    <h3>🌴 Updates to This Scroll</h3>
    <p>
        As time marches forward, so too shall our Privacy Scroll evolve. If any changes occur, you shall be notified by raven (or email).
    </p>

    <h3>📯 Contact the Wizard Lord</h3>
    <p>
        Should you have any questions, summon us at:
        <strong>Alireza.Pourkay@gmail.com</strong>.
    </p>

    <button class="elden-button" onclick="window.location.href='@Url.Action("Index", "Home")'">
        Return to Sanctuary 🏰
    </button>
</div>
